## Phase ordering rationale

Phases are ordered so each phase compiles and ships independently, and so the most important fixes (auth correctness, input validation, doc/reality reconciliation) land first while you still have the review fresh in your head.

1. **Phase 1 — Auth & doc correctness** (small, high signal)
